      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HAPPY DAD (1) hasn't been far away, finishing in the money twice in a row including last time in a Grade 5 at Sandown over 595m. Will find this more suitable and can atone. HECTOR DARCY (2) took the sit on the lead but levelled up to score (34.83) at this track in Grade 4/5 over 600m. The form out of his last race has been franked. Must be included in calculations. STARBORN (8) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 1.5 lengths back in third (29.72) at Sandown in a Restricted WIN over 515m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Will give a great sight again. IN MODERATION (6) won last start after racing on the pace. Sure to run well again.",
